Willard Robertson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Willard_Robertson 0 Willard Robertson (January 1, 1886 – April 5, 1948) was an American actor and writer. He appeared in 147 films between 1924 and 1948. He was born in Runnels, Texas and died in Hollywood, California.
